        <img class="img" data-func="responsiveImgSwitcher" data-desktopImg="https://www.worldvision.com.au" data-mobileImg="https://www.worldvision.com.au" />

</div>
        
    <p class="pad-top caption">
        <small>From gender-based violence to the burden of collecting water, different facets of gender inequality affect the lives of women and girls worldwide every day.</small>
    </p>

    </div>
</div><div class="module-block alternate">
    <div id="MainContentPlaceholder_C076_Col00" class="sf_colsIn container">

<a href="https://www.worldvision.com.au/gifts/products/WomenGirls/17-SEND-GIRL-TO-SCHOOL" class="cta-contextual descFirst text-center">
    <span class="icon"><img src="https://www.worldvision.com.au/images/default-source/Icons/1433990964491_icon-book.png?sfvrsn=33b5e33c_0&amp;quality=90&amp;maxheight=35&amp;resize=1" /></span>

